#19600
Entrance Hall of the Citadel of Kunji~
As you cross the threshold into the mighty citadel, the softly glowing
gates close behind you.  This entrance hall is lined with colossal
columns, crafted of the color-shifting rock that the monks favour.
Beautiful stained-glass windows, depicting various ancient legends and
forgotten tales, allow the bright sunlight of the valley to illuminate
the chamber.  Strangely, the windows are not visible when viewed from
outside.  The Citadel of Kunji is not without its tricks and traps.
~
