#19601
Intersection of Pathways~
You have come to an intersection of pathways.  To the east and west,
hallways lead onwards into the gargatuan structure.  Your way to
the north is blocked by a set of immense gilded ironwood doors, 
which stretch all the way to the ceiling.  Upon the doors is
inscribed the words "Jarreth Akn'e Aarn", which means nothing to you.
Surrounding the inscription are symbols representing the quartet of
Kunji: the gryphon, the dragon, the manticore and the phoenix.
~
