In the Shadow of the Altar~
This entire area of the chamber is shrouded in the shadow of the platform
floating high overhead.  A multitude of sweet-smelling candles provide
light in the darkness, allowing you to view the painted murals adorning
the walls.  There seems to be no apparent way to reach the floating
altar above you.  Perhaps you are not meant to violate its sacred
peace. 
~
