#19604
The Floating Altar~
The opulent splendour of the worship hall of the monks is spread
out below you.  It is only from this vantage point that you can
understand the brilliant pattern of candles arrayed below.  The lights
form a dazzling depiction of the Symbol of Kunji: a four-pointed star
with a smaller one within it.  The candles must be imbued with a
magical energy, for they never diminish in size or brightness.  It
is from here that the High Chanter, syl'Kronias leads the monks in
their fervent prayers and meditation.
~
