#19609
The Weaponsmithy~
  Rack upon rack of exquisitely forged weapons welcome you to the
weaponsmith's forge.  Swords and axes, pole arms and flails, all 
crafted with skill and experience wait expectantly for an owner.  A
hissing fills the room with steam, as another sword is cooled by the
smith.  Sweat pours down your temples, and you long for the peace and
tranquility of gentle silence.
  To the north, the rhythmic pounding of steel upon steel can be heard.
~
