#19610
A Store Room~
  This immense room is almost completely filled with crates, boxes, and
barrels of every size and description.  Every single article is 
meticulously labelled and arranged in a confusing system of organization.
Shelves of bottles, vials, and bags line the walls along with racks of
tools, implements and weapons.  While the room appears to be nearing
capacity, a powerful enchantment laid upon the chamber will prevent
it from ever becoming completely filled.
  The clamour of a mastersmith's hammer upon the anvil can be heard from
both the north and the south.
~
