#19627
The Kitchen~
  As you walk into the room, you are immediately immersed in the loud,
odour-rich environment that is the citadel's kitchen.  You are 
overwhelmed by the multitude of exotic, succulent dishes being 
expertly prepared by Kunji's finest chefs.  However, in addition to the
mouth-watering culinary delights being sped into the northern dining
room, a large vat of pasty grey gruel is being slowly stirred: a 
nourishing but unsatisfying meal for those of lesser standing.
  A large, framed sign is posted on the wall, attracting your attention.
  Swinging doors lead to the north and to the south.
~
